<h4><span>So what's next?</span></h4>
<p>I don't know! It took a lot off time to make this and I'm not sure when I'll be able to dedicate time for a different story-line. I just don't have anything planned currently but I do have ideas.</p>
<h4><span>Can I write/draw stuff for this?</span></h4>
<p>Please! Write anything you like on the AIAD or AICs. I'm very open to prequels, sequels, one-offs, artwork, and anything in between. Feel free to use the faces, formatting, and logos. I don't need attribution for them. Just give me a heads up so I can add things to the AIAD hub when they are made.</p>

